                Mr. Paton
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a1803b32-21a4-4f85-9ce1-214aa3b7806c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
